            <thetext>The current implementation of all data stores just take the loaded JSON data and create for the whole set of data a model. This can be in some cases a performance killer, especially if the application only needs a fraction of the received data.
The main idea is that the store should provide a way to manipulate the data before it is getting transformed in qooxdoo classes and objects.</thetext>
